  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Development Consultant (Recruitment)",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are a centrally located boutique recruitment firm experiencing strong growth. As the company scales, we are looking to bring on a Business Development Consultant (Recruitment) who can help support us through the next phase of the growth and development roadmap.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Highlights:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Start-up environment, welcoming workplace culture</li>\n  <li>Career growth and development opportunities</li>\n  <li>Convenient location (walking distance to Tanjong Pagar / Raffles Place MRT station)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Duties:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Developing connections and new sources of business and relationship management with existing accounts</li>\n  <li>Networking and building relationships with business partners and jobseekers</li>\n  <li>Identifying and pursuing new business opportunities to expand the client base</li>\n  <li>Managing key accounts to ensure the delivery standard and fulfilment level</li>\n  <li>Business partnering with internal stakeholders to improve current processes and implement new procedures</li>\n  <li>Conducting market research and competitive analysis to identify trends and opportunities for growth</li>\n  <li>Preparing and delivering presentations and proposals to potential clients</li>\n  <li>Developing strategies for brand promotion and lead generation</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma / Degree in Business Administration of Management</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of Sales / Business development experience</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Excellent time management and organizational skills</li>\n  <li>The potential candidate must be motivated to stay ahead by keeping up with the latest technological advancements and market trends.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates please email your resume to <strong>hr@recruitpedia.sg</strong> / <strong>talents@recruitpedia.sg</strong>  </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only the shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>EA License No.: 19C9682</p>\n<p><br></p>",
